### Get all products
GET http://localhost:8000/products

### Create a new product
POST http://localhost:8000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop",
  "price": 59999,
  "description": "A high-performance laptop for robotics work"
}

### Get a product by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE

### Update a product
PUT http://localhost:8000/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Laptop",
  "price": 64999
}

### Delete a product
DELETE http://localhost:8000/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
